PRE-REQUISTES
-------------

 * Philips TDA8008 development board for x86 platform
 * The simputer board for the arm platform
 * ISO7816-4 complaint smartcards following T=0 or T=1 protocol
 * Perl 5.5 or above for the Perl wrapper

COMPILING
---------

This distribution has currently been tested only on Linux/x86 and Linux/arm
based machines. There are 2 distributions provided: one for the arm and one
for x86.  Please go through the variables set in the makefiles, and change
them to point to the correct paths on your machine. Make sure that you have 
all the pre-requisites. Also you require to have SWIG installed for compiling
and the compilers/cross-compilers as well.
